parameters: //BG Name
$gameVariables.setValue(58, "AndreaDining");
//Map Name
$gameVariables.setValue(59, "AndreasHome");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Dinner was delicious, Andrea.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp.I’m glad you enjoyed it, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.And a wonderful wine pairing, as well.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp.Thank you, Andrea, I’m happy you liked it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp.I want you in the office early tomorrow. I need to brief you on everything we know about the Guild case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Of course. I'll be there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.Are you nervous about being on TV, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I can handle it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.Of course you can.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp.Good evening, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I'll see you tomorrow morning, Andrea.");
$PEOPLE-MC-Formal@(7)
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaOp^.Wow, that went really well.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp^.But I wonder just how seriously she took what I told her about Duncan and Charles.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp^.I hate the idea that I might be lying to the public on TV.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp^.At least I'll be doing it with a handsome mug...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp^.Is that what Andrea sees in me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.I hope that there’s more opportunity here than that. I know I could do more, if just given the chance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe^.I wonder how Melissa’s going to react to all this. Maybe after the interview, I should stay out of her sight for a while.");
$PEOPLE-MC-Jacket@(7)
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx>.The drinks are ready. I’d love your opinion on them, Miss Foxx.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.I’m not one to turn down a bit of alcohol.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp>.Nor am I.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaOp.Delicious!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Almost tastes like strawberries.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.Do I detect mint?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Family secrets, you two.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.As much as I’ve enjoyed the chit chat, I do believe we have an interview to conduct.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp.Don’t be so formal…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.You and 1Hero talk. I’ll go take the glasses to the kitchen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.Andrea brought you here to charm me, didn’t she?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Huh? I’m the Guild guy. I’m here to talk to you about the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe.So there is a connection?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There’s no connection. But, I know you think there could be.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe.Charles was a Guild leader. Just admit it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.If I knew that, I’d tell you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe.You would?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Not for free.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe.Oh, so you’re looking for a bribe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.Maybe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.Such a bad, bad officer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Maybe I’m just playing with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.Not yet, you aren't.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.You’re the one charming me, Miss Foxx.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlEx.Call me Kimberly, Detective Canbone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.Canmore…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.I didn’t expect you of all people to go over my head, Melissa.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx^.It was a tip. I didn’t know your operation was connected to the warehouse.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Like hell, you didn’t.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx^.Miss Kimura, we have Duncan’s henchmen in custody. We’ll find Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Nellie will find him, and when she does, we’re taking him out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe^.Hiding something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Excuse me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It doesn’t have to end this way, Andrea.");
$PEOPLE-Andrea@(7)
$PEOPLE-Andrea@(7)
$PEOPLE-MC-Jacket@(7)
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeShOp^.Damn… That was intense.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.I’m going to tell you something and you need to listen to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.We’re listening.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Melissa?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.Yes, I’m listening.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Nellie will find Duncan; and when she does, I will deal with him…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.You will no longer do ANYTHING in relation to the Eclipse Guild case. Do you understand, Miss Bhatt?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.I understand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.As for the arrests you’ve made, the suspects will be interrogated by my officers.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.As you wish.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.This is your one and final warning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe^.Understood.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Go home, Melissa. Enjoy your evening.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp^.Is 1Hero back on the force?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Go home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp^.Yes, ma’am.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.It’s time you know the truth, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The truth?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Duncan will be allowed to run the Eclipse Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McVo./shock");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.We’re letting him get away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Why? I thought the Guild was close to death.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.The Guild is a recruiter of murderers and thieves. Until recently, the organization was split into twelve distinct groups.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Duncan is the last man standing, isn’t he?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Correct, 1Hero. And now we have an opportunity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe.But… why?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.It’s a honeypot, 1Hero. Don’t you see?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.We’re using the Guild as a trap?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.It’s been the plan all along. We’re not killing the Guild… We’re…. restructuring it to our advantage.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Damn… What about Nellie?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.Nellie has become quite the valuable asset.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.She just wants her freedom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.If it wasn’t for me, she’d be rotting in jail for another decade…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.She owes me much more than what she’s paid.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.She should know what’s going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.I’ll be the judge of what information she needs to do her job.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.As for you, 1Hero… You’ll have new cases, fed by the honeypot.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.And Melissa will know about them?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Your cover’s been blown… You’re back on the force.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.Is there something you want to say?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I want to be on the Guild case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.You’re still working for me, 1Hero. Don’t worry about that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.So you’re simply going to have Nellie report on Duncan?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.She’s gotten good at it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Another rough night outside. You better get home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Looks like the weather is starting to turn. You better get home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.See you at the station tomorrow?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.You’ve got a lot of work ahead of you, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiShCl.I… I don’t know what came over me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe>.Not exactly the most professional behavior, Miss Foxx.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx.I’m not like this… I just got carried away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx>.1Hero would be quite the catch for any woman. I don’t blame you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiShCl.No… No… This was a bad idea.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx>.Don’t worry, Kimberly…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp>.We’ve known each other a long time now. Your secret is safe with me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx.It won’t happen again… I value our relationship, commissioner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx>.There, there. Nothing to worry about. We’ve got your back, Miss Foxx.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaOp.Thank you… And I’m sorry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I… Uhh…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp>.I’ll speak with you later, Mr. Canmore.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrEx.It’s been a lovely visit. But I should get back to the office.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx>.Don’t you want an interview about the thieves that broke into the Wilkes’ mansion?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.Perhaps another time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx>.I trust you will not report on any activities without first allowing us to comment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.I’m working on a story… about Charles Wilkes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.What are you reporting?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx>.Call me tomorrow, Kimberly. I’ll give you everything I know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFrOp.Thank you, Miss Kimura.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaOp.Thanks for the drink. It was lovely.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx>.Any time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Andrea! I’m sorry…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.You were perfect, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Huh?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.You’re learning fast.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.But… I didn’t do anything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.On the contrary. Our relationship with Channel 4 grows closer with the two of you entangled.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.But, is this… blackmail?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp.What!? Of course not!...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.To get along with the media you have to play the game, and that game requires you to get close with Kimberly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe.Am I being clear?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I just never expected police work to lead to this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx.Consider yourself lucky. Some officers lose their life in the line of duty…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.I merely ask you to bust a nut or two.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Wow… I guess I understand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp.You won’t let me down, 1Hero. You’re too perfect for this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx.Now get back to work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Yes, ma’am.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.If you have any concerns, feel free to stop by and talk.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Of course, Miss Kimura.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdVo./order");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.And that’s why we believe that Charles Wilkes was connected to the Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.It’s only a matter of time before Duncan Helmer makes some sort of move on the mansion…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.There is something he wants there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe^.Shit. This is going to make us look bad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.How Charles went undetected for so long… It’s shocking.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.The most important thing we can do now is to let our undercover operation get evidence.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Isn’t there enough? Couldn’t we make a move now and arrest Duncan?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe^.No. Duncan is the tip of the iceberg. We let him make his move.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.What about Lillian?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaDe^.Do you have a suggestion?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Lillian is involved… I don’t know how, but Madalyn Rose is working with her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We’re still working on the Rose case. She may be here in North Santiva.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.She is definitely here in North Santiva.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx^.We have to keep this under wraps…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnDe^.Foxx is on our side, but Paul is digging for a story.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.What do you want me to do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.Keep Kimberly on our side. Do whatever you have to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.Not a problem.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.And just how long do you expect we can keep this up?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.This is on Canmore now. He’ll do what he needs to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.I want to be there for the interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp^.Absolutely not. We’re keeping a low profile…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.1Hero will do this alone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.But, Miss Kimura…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx^.It’s the weekend Melissa. Go and enjoy it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I can handle this, Miss Bhatt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.So what’s the plan? How do we spin this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.The Wilkes mansion was searched by officers in connection with a stolen painting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.You’re referring to the search warrant issued in 2002?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp^.Correct.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.It was believed that a stolen Rembrandt was being stored in the Wilkes' treasure room.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.But upon further search, no evidence was found that Wilkes housed any illegal artwork.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.So how does it connect with the break in?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.I think it would be a safe assumption that the thieves were after the stolen piece.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.So we spin the story that Wilkes was hiding the artwork all along?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp^.That’s the plan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.It’s believable, but what would be the ramifications of dragging the Wilkes name through the mud?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Lillian won't be happy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.You suspect that Wilkes was connected to the Eclipse Guild. Your suspicions are not unfounded.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Do you know something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.We’re learning as we go. Duncan Helmer wants something from Charles. A stolen Rembrandt may as well be the prize he seeks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Eventually the truth will have to come out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.You let me worry about that. Can you handle this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McVo./solve");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp^.Good.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Good luck, 1Hero. I hope you have what it takes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.Of course he does. I’m sure you’ve seen his potential.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.Go to Channel 4 now, 1Hero. Get ready and put on the charm with Kim…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.I’ll meet you there later.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.I thought he was going this alone?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.He’ll be alone in the interview.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I’ll head over and talk with Kimberly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrOp^.Come. I’ll walk you two out.");
black
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaOp.So… The underground room… It leads to a world of demons?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.It doesn't surprise me that something demonic is happening there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiWoEx^.The room has a gateway to Hell… But it can only be opened with specific animal parts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I mean… We saw something down there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.There’s also a secret passage near the kitchen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.What are you going to do, Miss Kimura?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Of course, we’re investigating it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaEx^.Thank you! My producer thinks I’m crazy. But you are one of the only other people who has seen it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Where are my manners? Let me get you all some drinks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErFrOp.I could go for a drink.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiHaOp^.Thank you, Miss Kimura.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Andrea doesn’t give two shits about the rift. You’re stepping on her toes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiVo^./shock");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.You should have kept this between us. There is an undercover operation going on in the mansion right now…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.That’s why you aren’t allowed to trespass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.I think this is bigger than the Guild case… Maybe Andrea can protect us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.I don’t trust her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.I’m sure you have much more to tell me about these demons… I want to hear all about it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Is someone at the door?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.I wonder who that could be.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp^.Expecting company?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx.Get dressed. We have another guest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Can I break open this jar?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McVo./fail");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.This vase is made of metal. I’m not strong enough to break it open.");
